Uses of Interface
org.cojen.tupl.repl.Replicator

  • Packages that use Replicator 
    Package Description
    org.cojen.tupl.repl
    General-purpose Raft-based replication system, intended for supporting fully replicated databases.

    • Uses of Replicator in org.cojen.tupl.repl

      Subinterfaces of Replicator in org.cojen.tupl.repl 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      interface  DatabaseReplicator
      Implementation of a ReplicationManager for supporting full database replication.
      interface  DirectReplicator
      Replicator interface for applications which directly control the replication data, and are also responsible for processing snapshots.
      interface  MessageReplicator
      Message-oriented replication interface, which is a bit easier to use than StreamReplicator.
      interface  StreamReplicator
      Low-level replication interface, which receives messages in a non-delineated stream.
